---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - TheBestOffersAround.com">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Last Updated: November 15, 2025</p>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          When you visit TheBestOffersAround.com, we may collect certain information including:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Email address (if you subscribe to our newsletter)</li>
          <li>Browser type and version</li>
          <li>Pages visited and time spent on site</li>
          <li>Referring website addresses</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the collected information to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Send you newsletters and promotional content (if subscribed)</li>
          <li>Improve our website and user experience</li>
          <li>Analyze site traffic and usage patterns</li>
          <li>Comply with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          We use cookies to enhance your browsing experience. Cookies are small files stored on 
          your device that help us understand how you interact with our site. You can disable 
          cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect site functionality.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">4. Third-Party Links</h2>
        <p>
          Our website contains affiliate links to third-party products and services. When you click 
          these links and make a purchase, we may earn a commission. We are not responsible for the 
          privacy practices of these third-party sites.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>
          We implement appropriate security measures to protect your personal information. However, 
          no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee 
          absolute security.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mt-4">
          <li>Access your personal information</li>
          <li>Correct inaccurate data</li>
          <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
          <li>Unsubscribe from our newsletter at any time</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page 
          with an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">8. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>
          If you have questions about this privacy policy, please 
          <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact us</a>.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
